<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1741299-could-it-be-that-thomas-hauser-is-an">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Could it be that Thomas Hauser is an imaginery friend (alter ego) of Max Aue? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
