      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/141301.Jonathan_Littell">About Jonathan Littell</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/141301.Jonathan_Littell"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1530616182p3/141301.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/141301.Jonathan_Littell">Jonathan Littell
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
286
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer10621551406901749110">A bi-lingual (English / French) writer living in Barcelona. He is a dual citizen of the United States and France and is of Jewish background. His first novel written in French, <i>
  <b>Les Bienveillantes</b>
</i>, won two major French awards. <br/><br/>His father is the writer <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/101398._Robert_Littell' title=' Robert Littell' rel='nofollow noopener'> Robert Littell</a>, also resident in France and who authored numerous spy novels.</span>
  <span id="freeText10621551406901749110" style="display:none">A bi-lingual (English / French) writer living in Barcelona. He is a dual citizen of the United States and France and is of Jewish background. His first novel written in French, <i>
  <b>Les Bienveillantes</b>
</i>, won two major French awards. <br /><br />His father is the writer <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/101398._Robert_Littell" title=" Robert Littell" rel="nofollow noopener"> Robert Littell</a>, also resident in France and who authored numerous spy novels.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10621551406901749110" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

