          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;If you were born in a country or at a time not only when nobody comes to kill your wife and your children, but also nobody comes to ask you to kill the wives and children of others, then render thanks to God and go in peace. But always keep this thought in mind: you might be luckier than I, but you’re not a better person.&rdquo;</span>
